<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201008/2af2780d3a6a4d2eaef2ea91e664e3f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>【沙胆彪碳炉牛杂煲】</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>📍店铺地址:</strong></p>
