<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>滋粥楼小馆///</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201008/929bd8857e2f4d54869bdfa343d88fc2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">代表顺德的粥水火锅、桑拿鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">出了广东就难吃到了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201008/c279c98246274d2f925d5527c699b050.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
